Description: Fungarium facilitates the use of digitized fungal collections (i.e. fungarium specimens) or observations (e.g. iNaturalist, MushroomObserver) for taxonomic, geographic, and temporal analyses of ecological traits in fungi (e.g. habitat, host, substrate associations).
